    <body>
      <lg type="sonnet">
        <lg type="1st quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>Within winds the sea leads to the shore,</l>
            <l>as well as time goes further,</l>
            <l>every place we have been changes,</l>
            <l>when you are fightin for something progress comes within time</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="2nd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>life begins with <add>the important</add> birth</l>
            <l><choice><orig>smal</orig><reg>small</reg></choice> steps lead to success</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>time allows to make progress</l>
            <l>time allows two different aspects life and progress, and death</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="3rd quatrain">
          <s>
            <l>time is more powerful than just beauty</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>it lets beauty fade when you are getting older</l>
          </s>
          <s>
            <l>death is part of nature cycle</l>
            <l>everything is uncertain despite of death</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
        <lg type="final couplet">
          <s>
            <l>this sonnet will exist overtime</l>
            <l>its value is not describable.</l>
          </s>
        </lg>
      </lg>
